76561198084061381,Recommended,569610,31060334,Posted: 10 April,all,JPox,"What can I say about this game that hasn't been said already. I liked the variety in enemy formations and even though it is a space invaders ripoff, I enjoyed  the simplistic gameplay a lot. If you came to this game for an easy 100%, you are in the wrong place. It is important to know that you will never complete this game. Never have I seen achievements be so straight foreward yet be so impossible. All in all for the price that I bought it for (couple of cents) this game was insanely difficult (just wait for lvl 15) and a lot of fun. Recommended for people with inhuman reaction speed and a lot of spare time."
